## EP2

###Before start
    Account in LAADS DAAC (https://ladsweb.modaps.eosdis.nasa.gov/)
    wget (www.gnu.org/software/wget/)
    PC/HPC server (recommend)

###Steps:
    Select tiles – submit request – get the download code
    PC or HPC server 

###Tricks
    How to effectively download thousands of tiles

### For details please check the video in [BiliBili](https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1G44y1P7Ts) or [Youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xmTW9psiFWU&list=PL8B89O7x7hGign7l0M93WsHcvnJdilp9G&index=2&t=1s).

